<paragraph blockId="352.[151,1436,150,860]" pageId="352" pageNumber="353">
REMARKS: 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[270,507,726,753]" pageId="352" pageNumber="353" refId="ref368882" refString="Rondani, C. (1861 e) Dipterologiae italicae prodromus. Vol. IV. Species italicae ordinis dipterorum in genera characteribus definita, ordinatim collectae, methodo analatica distinctae, et novis vel minus cognitis descriptis. Pars tertia: Muscidae. Tachininarum complementum. A. Stocchi. Parmae [= Parma], 174 pp." type="book" year="1861">Rondani (1861e: 65)</bibRefCitation>
proposed 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1861" box="[631,847,727,752]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Polypodiaceae" genus="Pyrrosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Polypodiales" pageId="352" pageNumber="353" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="segregata">
<emphasis box="[631,847,727,752]" italics="true" pageId="352" pageNumber="353">Pyrrosia segregata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
for 
<taxonomicName authority="Meigen, 1824 sensu Rondani (1856: 72)" authorityName="Rondani" authorityPageNumber="72" authorityYear="1856" class="Insecta" family="Rhinophoridae" genus="Tachina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="352" pageNumber="353" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pacifica">
<emphasis box="[900,1090,726,752]" italics="true" pageId="352" pageNumber="353">Tachina pacifica</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Meigen, J. W." box="[1100,1259,726,752]" pageId="352" pageNumber="353" refId="ref359357" refString="Meigen, J. W. (1824) Systematische Beschreibung der bekannten europaischen zweiflugeligen Insekten. Vierter Theil. Schulz- Wundermann, Hamm, xii + 428 pp." type="book" year="1824">Meigen, 1824</bibRefCitation>
<emphasis box="[1269,1331,727,752]" italics="true" pageId="352" pageNumber="353">sensu</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." pageId="352" pageNumber="353" refId="ref368338" refString="Rondani, C. (1856) Dipterologiae italicae prodromus. Vol: I. Genera italica ordinis dipterorum ordinatim disposita et distincta et in familias et stirpes aggregata. A. Stocchi, Parmae [= Parma], 226 pp. + [2] pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 8160" type="book" year="1856">Rondani (1856: 72)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, which he considered a new species. Rondani (1861: 65) described both sexes of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1861" box="[1223,1436,763,788]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Polypodiaceae" genus="Pyrrosia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Polypodiales" pageId="352" pageNumber="353" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="segregata">
<emphasis box="[1223,1436,763,788]" italics="true" pageId="352" pageNumber="353">Pyrrosia segregata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
without specifying the exact 
<taxonomicName box="[526,612,798,824]" family="Number" pageId="352" pageNumber="26" rank="family">number</taxonomicName>
of specimens and not giving a range of lengths. We found 
<specimenCount box="[1282,1436,798,825]" pageId="352" pageNumber="353" type="generic" typeStatus="syntypes">nine syntypes</specimenCount>
in this study.
</paragraph>
